Posted @withregram • @meemaestee1 I attended the opening of the Hajj & Umrah Conference and Exhibition 2023 #HajjExpo, alongside my husband, the chairman NAHCON, & his team and other Nigerian dignitaries on monday, the 9th Of January, in Jeddah, the kingdom Of Saudi Arabia. 
It was a heartfelt experience where I met some dignitaries, from Saudi Arabia, Egypt, Dubai and other parts of the countries. 
I was also privileged and honored to meet the Chief Imam and Khateeb of Masjid Al Haram of Makkah (Sheikh Abdul Rehman Al Sudais), Masha Allah. 
The Hajj Minister (Tawfig Al-Rabiah) announced that #Hajj1444 will return to pre-pandemic numbers without any age restrictions, as it was before the coronavirus pandemic. 
What a good way to start the year 2023, Alhamdulillah 😇
